    "en": {
      "title": "Mistral and Havells Air Fryers by Abans, all-in-one solution for gas shortage",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The Mistral and Havells Air Fryers are all-in-one healthy cooking appliances that address gas, energy and health issues. A guaranteed game-changer in the kitchen, one can cook, bake, grill, toast, roast, defrost and reheat using the Mistral and Havells Air Fryers available at Abans.",
        "The Mistral Air Fryer combines efficiency with quality, to produce restaurant-quality meals for the entire family. Mistral and Havells Air Fryers by Abans afford guilt-free cooking, without having to compromise one\u2019s health. For instance, they allow one to enjoy deep-fried delicacies by taking deep-frying out of the equation. Frying using both Mistral and Havells Air Fryers is 80% less oily compared to traditional deep frying, as they enable frying without the use of oil. Leaving food crispy, it maintains the perfect balance between taste and health.",
        "The Mistral Air Fryer comes with an easy-to-use manual control panel, adjustable cooking times and temperatures and features the innovative Rapid Air Technology that helps cook food evenly. The Havells Digital Air Fryer, with its digital display, adds a touch of elegance to the kitchen. It comes with the patented round basket, equipped with slots on the side wall for better air circulation. Its integrated timer with an auto-off and a temperature control function allows precise cooking with a 60-minute timer, with a temperature setting of up to 200 \u00b0C. Its innovative air filtration system filters out unpleasant odours, leaving the kitchen extremely clean and odourless. With the 4L pan capacity, Havells\u2019 air frying basket comes with a separator that lets one cook multiple food items simultaneously, saving time. Both Mistral and Havells Air Fryers afford the peace of mind that comes with a two-year iron-clad warranty.",
        "Using an Air Fryer is a simple, yet extremely effective healthy cooking solution one can adopt right at home and is an ideal solution for the cooking gas crisis. Mistral and Havells Air Fryers are available at any Abans showroom and www.BuyAbans.com, with island wide doorstep delivery. Call the hotline 0115 999 000 for more details on products, special offers and deals."
      ],
